Federal Reserve System (pp. 268–69)

Enforcement Actions: Cite written agreements resulting from enforcement actions as: Written Agreement Between <private bank name> and <Federal Reserve Bank name>, Dkt. No. <docket number> (<date>).

Written Agreement Between Ridgedale State Bank and Federal Reserve Bank of Minneapolis, Dkt. No. 03-024-WA/RB-SM (July 29, 2003).
